OL,3,CVodafone and Three #15bn merger could
OL,4,Cget green light, UK watchdog says
OL,6,FThe watchdog had concerns that the
OL,7,Fmerger could lead to higher prices for
OL,8,Fcustomers and harm the position of
OL,9,Fvirtual network operators such as Sky
OL,10,FMobile and Lebara.
OL,12,FBut on Tuesday, the CMA said it had
OL,13,Foutlined certain actions to be taken
OL,14,Fby the combined group that were likely
OL,15,Fto address its concerns.
OL,17,FThis included committing to plans to
OL,18,Fupgrade the UK's mobile network
OL,19,Finfrastructure over the next eight
OL,20,Fyears, which would become a legal
OL,21,Fobligation overseen by regulators.
