OL,3,CVodafone and Three #15bn merger could
OL,4,Cget green light, UK watchdog says
OL,6,F"Our provisional view is that binding
OL,7,Fcommitments combined with short-term
OL,8,Fprotections for consumers and
OL,9,Fwholesale providers would address our
OL,10,Fconcerns while preserving the benefits
OL,11,Fof this merger."
OL,13,FVodafone and Three said they believe
OL,14,Fthe CMA's provisional findings provide
OL,15,F"a path to final clearance" of their
OL,16,Fmerger plans.
OL,18,F"The merger will be a catalyst for
OL,19,Fpositive change," spokespeople for the
OL,20,Ffirms said.
