OL,3,CVodafone and Three #15bn merger could
OL,4,Cget green light, UK watchdog says
OL,6,F"It will bring significant benefits to
OL,7,Fbusinesses and consumers throughout
OL,8,Fthe UK, and it will bring advanced 5G
OL,9,Fto every school and hospital across
OL,10,Fthe country.
OL,12,F"The merger is also closely aligned
OL,13,Fwith the Government's mission to drive
OL,14,Fgrowth and to encourage more private
OL,15,Finvestment in the UK."
OL,17,FRuss Mould, investment director at AJ
OL,18,FBell, said the potential green light
OL,19,Fwould be a "game-changer" for Vodafone.
