OL,6,F"Vodafone had banked on the merger
OL,7,Fbeing its ticket to regaining strength
OL,8,Fin the UK, boosting its customer
OL,9,Fnumbers and triggering investment in a
OL,10,Fbetter mobile experience for users.
OL,12,F"Assuming it agrees to the competition
OL,13,Fauthority's demands, Vodafone could be
OL,14,Fat the forefront of a radical
OL,15,Freshaping of the UK mobile network
OL,16,Finfrastructure.
OL,18,F"However, significant spending will
OL,19,Finevitably lead to higher prices for
OL,20,Fconsumers down the line, so the merger
OL,21,Fisn't necessarily good for everyone."
